results.question: Find the semester when both Master students and Bachelor students got enrolled in.

results.gen_sql: select s.semester_id, s.semester_name from semesters s join student_enrolment se on s.semester_id = se.semester_id join degree_programs dp on se.degree_program_id = dp.degree_program_id group by s.semester_id, s.semester_name having max(case when upper(dp.degree_summary_name) like '%master%' then 1 else 0 end) = 1 and max(case when upper(dp.degree_summary_name) like '%bachelor%' then 1 else 0 end) = 1

results.gen_sql: select semesters.semester_id from semesters join student_enrolment on semesters.semester_id = student_enrolment.semester_id join degree_programs on student_enrolment.degree_program_id = degree_programs.degree_program_id where degree_programs.degree_summary_name in ('masters', 'bachelors') group by semesters.semester_id having count(distinct degree_programs.degree_summary_name) = 2
